# Galileo Protocol — Environment Variables
#
# This is the monorepo root .env.example. Each app has its own:
#   apps/api/.env.example          → API server (copy to apps/api/.env)
#   .env.testnet.example           → Full-stack testnet / blockchain config
#
# Quick start:
#   cp apps/api/.env.example apps/api/.env
#
# Required for tests:
#   DATABASE_URL_TEST=postgresql://galileo:galileo_dev@localhost:5432/galileo_test
